# Celiums Memory — Code owners
# Implements ADR-018 §"Required hardening — Required reviewers".
#
# Rules:
# - Every path needs at least one owner.
# - Security-sensitive paths require 2 maintainer approvals (enforced
#   via branch protection rules at the GitHub-org level).
# - Governance docs require BDFL sign-off.

# ── Default owner ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
